application_type_full: Approval of details reserved by a condition (discharge)
description: Submission of energy performance certificates part pursuant  to condition 23 part E, of planning permission ref: 204095VAR dated 26/03/2021 for 'Application for a Minor Material Amendment (S73a) to vary conditions: 2 (approved drawings); 18 (cycle parking); 23b (design of LZC equipment); 24 (details of communal plant); 26 (post-construction energy monitoring) and 27 (sustainable design and construction) of planning permission ref: 194353FUL dated 20/03/2020 (as amended by 203082NMA, dated 21/08/2020 and 203277NMA, dated 22/09/2020) for: Construction of buildings up to nine-storey in height to provide residential. With vehicle access from Central Parade/ Western Avenue, amenity spaces, refuse and recycling storage and soft landscaping. Amendment seeks one additional 1 bed flat, erection of electricity substation, reduction in size of  the amenity space, amendments to fenestration on the north elevation, additional fenestration on the east elevation, amendment provides further details to satisfy conditions 18, 23b, 24 and 27 of planning permission 194353FUL.',
